@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram

state "Create Account" as CreateAccount
CreateAccount : entry / User starts
CreateAccount : do / Fill details
CreateAccount : exit / Account created

state "Watch Videos" as WatchVideos
WatchVideos : entry / User logged in
WatchVideos : do / Watch videos
WatchVideos : exit / Video watched

state "Upload Videos" as UploadVideos
UploadVideos : entry / User logged in
UploadVideos : do / Upload video
UploadVideos : exit / Video uploaded

state "Save Videos" as SaveVideos
SaveVideos : entry / User logged in
SaveVideos : do / Save video in likes list
SaveVideos : exit / Video saved

state "View Likes List" as ViewLikesList
ViewLikesList : entry / User logged in
ViewLikesList : do / View saved videos
ViewLikesList : exit / Videos viewed

state "Enter Discussion" as EnterDiscussion
EnterDiscussion : entry / User logged in
EnterDiscussion : do / Enter discussion
EnterDiscussion : exit / Discussion entered

state "Idle" <<choice>>
state "Invalid User" <<choice>>

[*] --> CreateAccount

CreateAccount --> WatchVideos : [Logged in]
CreateAccount --> InvalidUser : [Not logged in]

WatchVideos --> [*] : [Logged out]

InvalidUser --> CreateAccount : [Create Account]
InvalidUser --> WatchVideos : [Login]

UploadVideos --> [*] : [Logged out]

InvalidUser --> UploadVideos : [Login]

SaveVideos --> [*] : [Logged out]

InvalidUser --> SaveVideos : [Login]

ViewLikesList --> [*] : [Logged out]

InvalidUser --> ViewLikesList : [Login]

EnterDiscussion --> [*] : [Logged out]

InvalidUser --> EnterDiscussion : [Login]

Idle --> CreateAccount : [Create Account]
Idle --> WatchVideos : [Watch Videos]
Idle --> UploadVideos : [Upload Videos]
Idle --> SaveVideos : [Save Videos]
Idle --> ViewLikesList : [View Likes List]
Idle --> EnterDiscussion : [Enter Discussion]

InvalidUser --> Idle : [Logged in]

CreateAccount --> InvalidUser : [Invalid action]

WatchVideos --> InvalidUser : [Invalid action]

UploadVideos --> InvalidUser : [Invalid action]

SaveVideos --> InvalidUser : [Invalid action]

ViewLikesList --> InvalidUser : [Invalid action]

EnterDiscussion --> InvalidUser : [Invalid action]

InvalidUser <<choice>>
InvalidUser --> CreateAccount : [Create Account]
InvalidUser --> WatchVideos : [Login]
InvalidUser --> UploadVideos : [Login]
InvalidUser --> SaveVideos : [Login]
InvalidUser --> ViewLikesList : [Login]
InvalidUser --> EnterDiscussion : [Login]

@enduml
